init vars
create a grade book
display the grades and stats
===
initialize an array of grades to a fixed size
create a grade book for "CS101 C++ Programming" using the grades just created
display a welcome message
display the grade book's stats
===
using a fixed size defined in the class GradeBook, create an array of grades
  87,68,94,100,83,78,85,91,76,87
create a GradeBook object, passing "CS101 C++ Programming" and the grades above to the constructor
call the objects welcome message
call the objects function to display stats
